fields.title: Object oriented programming with Python
fields.overview:
This course introduces advanced programming skills and focuses on the core concepts
of object-oriented programming and design using a high-level language, either Python
or Java. Object-oriented programming represents the integration of software
components into a large-scale software architecture.

fields.title: Kazakhstan History
fields.overview: Choose from a range of different topics that interest you, from politics in the Roman Republic to material culture in the Ottoman Empire and neoliberalism.

fields.title: Base Math
fields.overview: Mathematics is rich and stimulating and develops logical reasoning, analysis, problem solving skills, creativity and the ability to think in abstract ways.
